ygData.messageBody:
Hello,

There is a new survey for the eqbards community.

If you are a subscriber to the EQ Bards list,
please tell us what server you play on. If you
play on more than one, try to limit your answers
to your primary 3.

----

o Bertoxxulous
o Brell Serilis

To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://www.onelist.com/surveys/eqbards

Note: Please do not reply to this message. Survey votes are not collected
via email. To vote, you must go to the ONElist website.


Thanks!

eqbards Owner
